					<h2>The Ministry And Its Departments</h2>
					<p>The Department of Defence deals with the Integrated Defence Staff (IDS) and three Services and various Inter Service Organisations.
						The Department of Defence Research and Development is headed by a Secretary, who is the Scientific Adviser to the Raksha Mantri.
					The Department of Ex-Servicemen Welfare is headed by a Secretary and deals with all resettlement, welfare and pensionary matters of Ex-Servicemen.</p>
